e is 'not hermetic', as noted by the Israeli military. As a precautionary measure, the transportation of hazardous materials has been restricted to several factories in the north, and a factory producing ice cream in Acre has ceased operations: the ammonia gas used there can be hazardous in the event of an attack. Israel intends to prevent Iran from repeating the scenario of April 13-14, when in response to a strike on the Iranian consulate in Damascus, hundreds of drones and rockets were launched at Israel. According to CNN, the Iranian response may also include attacks on American forces in Iraq and Syria. Proxy militias in this region have been attacking US targets for months. However, after January, when a drone killed three American soldiers in Jordan, the attacks subsided. An Iranian order may revive them. A decision on the relocation of American troops has not been made yet. The potential strike group of the aircraft carrier Theodore Roosevelt may be relocated from the Omani Gulf to the Aden or Red Sea.
